"title": "5953: stability",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5953",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The state of being in a firm or unwavering situation, whether emotional, political or personal. Stability is an important element of a settled life before God.</p>\n<h2>Stability in the life of faith</h2>\n<h3>Stability for the believer is based on God's unchanging nature</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut32:4\">DEU 32:4</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps103:19\">PSA 103:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam2:2\">1SA 2:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam22:32\">2SA 22:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job25:2\">JOB 25:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps62:2\">PSA 62:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps89:2\">PSA 89:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps93:2\">PSA 93:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa26:4\">ISA 26:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt7:24-Matt7:27\">MAT 7:24–7:27</a></p>\n<h3>Stability gives resistance to spiritual assault</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor16:13\">1CO 16:13</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:22-Col1:23\">COL 1:22–1:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps20:7-Ps20:8\">PSA 20:7–20:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps40:2\">PSA 40:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov10:25\">PRO 10:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt10:22\">MAT 10:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom16:25\">ROM 16:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:58\">1CO 15:58</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor1:24\">2CO 1:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal5:1\">GAL 5:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil1:27\">PHP 1:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil1:27\">PHP 1:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col4:12\">COL 4:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess3:8\">1TH 3:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess2:15\">2TH 2:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb6:19\">HEB 6:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:23\">HEB 10:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:23-Jas1:25\">JAS 1:23–1:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas5:8\">JAS 5:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet1:12\">2PE 1:12</a></p>\n<h3>Stability depends upon firmness of faith</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col2:5-Col2:7\">COL 2:5–2:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps57:7\">PSA 57:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:5\">PSA 119:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa26:3\">ISA 26:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph3:17\">EPH 3:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb3:14\">HEB 3:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet5:9-1Pet5:10\">1PE 5:9–5:10</a></p>\n<h3>Stability is an important aim of Christian ministry</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:14\">EPH 4:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:28\">COL 1:28</a></p>\n<h2>Political stability</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam7:16\">2SA 7:16</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov29:4\">PRO 29:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam13:13\">1SA 13:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam5:12\">2SA 5:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs2:12\">1KI 2:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov16:12\">PRO 16:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa16:5\">ISA 16:5</a></p>",
